audio_descriptions.notes:
Mr Bean, yawns out his window
 Mrs Wickit exits the house, walks down the stairs using her cane while a small girl approaches the house with newspapers.
The small girl proceeds to the door and Mr. Bean notices through the window and heads towards the door. Before grabbing his paper, Mr. Bean gets caught up in looking at himself through the mirror   
He tries to fix his hair but fails.
he then reaches out to grab his newspaper, but it slips back out the mail slot.
Confused, mr bean looks through the door slot 
finding nothing, he opens the door and takes a step out to look around
he gives up and closes the door
the screen fades to black
The next day, mr bean yawns out his window and sees the small girl with the newspaper approach his door
he heads for the door more rapidly
fixes his hair in the mirror once
then reaches to grab the paper only to have it slip out again
confused and frustrated, Mr Bean steps outside and looks around to find no one
the screen fades to black
the next day, mr bean yawns out his window, and immediately sees the small girl approach the door with the newspaper. He runs downstairs and heads straight to the newspaper only to have it slip out again.
Infuriated, mr bean opens the door to find no one
the screen fades to black
It is the end screen with a picture Mr. Bean in the background. And in a smaller box it shows a snippet of the next video which is mr bean giving himself a haircut.
A note saying watch more appears with arrows pointing to the words "next video" and "subscribe"
